review_text: Nice
Nice small greenery area to have lunch in the shade. The small-children zone is closed off, so safe for them, and they are not in grown ups lounging zone.  Several benches near play area.
All you need for a quick run with your kids!
Nice little park for kids, also has some picnic tables.
Great snoozing spot...
Very nice park.
Great shaded playground for kids on a hot summer day.
A cool small place to stop by

(Translated by Google) A nice little park around the corner that my 5 year old kids considered to be a playpen (as far as games are concerned) so for the latter - the games - let's say there is better somewhere else for kids in this area. age but for adults there is a picnic table, a few benches, a few trees and surprisingly a kind of wooden bed ... (Being an itinerant I would make my bed of choice) ... that said on Fridays and Saturday evenings (nights), due to the club diagonally, the park is full of drunk and loud people. Park all the same well kept and pleasant at strategic times.

(Original)
Un beau petit parc de coin de rue que mes enfants de 5 ans ont considéré être un parc pour bébé (pour ce qui est des jeux) donc pour ces derniers - les jeux - disons qu'il y a mieux ailleurs pour des enfants de cet âge mais pour des adultes il y a une table de pic-nic, quelques bancs, quelques arbres et surprenament une sorte de lit en bois... (Être itinérant j'en ferais mon lit de choix) ...cela dit les vendredi et samedi soirs (nuits), en raison du club en diagonale, le parc est plein de gens saouls et bruyants. Parc tout de même bien tenu et agréable aux heures stratégiques.
